Popular Ghanaian singer, Stonebwoy shares cute photo with his wife Louisa Satekla as he calls her a true friend . The two are really dishing out couple goals as Stonebwoy was seen listening to his wife, Louisa while she speaks. We recall, Stonebwoy revealed he married before having a child to avoid unnecessary “baby mama drama” that comes with having a baby out of wedlock. Stonebwoy married Dr Louisa Ansong on Friday, June 16, 2017 in Accra. They have a beautiful daughter named Catherine Jidula T. Satekla together. He wrote: “A True Friend, Who Can Find! Pay Attention To Details.. Journey Of Life!!”